Title: A certification of Peterson's algorithm for managing mutual exclusion
Author: Eduardo Gim√©nez
Institution: INRIA Rocquencourt
Description: This is a proof of certification of Peterson's algorithm
for managing mutual exclusion. The case of two processes is treated
in the directory called ``binary'' (see the README file in this
directory). The case of n processes will be available soon.
Keywords: mutual exclusion, concurrency, Peterson's algorithm,
